ActIndian Act
SubjectSakimay First Nations ** DESIGNATION ** For leasing purposes
PrecisOrder accepting a DESIGNATION wherein the SAKIMAY FIRST NATIONS surrender, for a term of 50 years, some 5.041 hectares (12.46 acres) of land on Shesheep Indian Reserve No. 74A and 116.573 hectares (288.05 acres) of land on Sakimay Indian Reserve No. 74-6, in Saskatchewan, for leasing purposes.
